                :host([open]) {
                    display: block;

                    pointer-events: none;
                    filter: var(--disabled-filter, grayscale(100%));
                }

                input[type="number"] {

                    margin: 8px;
                    padding: 4px;
                    width: 36px;

                    height: 100%;

                    height: 100%;
                    width: 100%;
                    font-size: 14px;
                    display: none;
                }

                #settings .setting-option{
                    margin-bottom: 12px;
                }

                #webcam-error {
                    height: 320px;

                    font-size: 14px;
                    color: #1967D2;
                    text-align: center;
                    width: 240px;
                }

                    --color: #fff;
                    --background-color: #1967D2;

                input[type="number"] {

                    padding: 0;
